wiki.text:
'PFS' can stand for:

'Finance': *The Personal Finance Society, one of the largest professional bodies
for financial advisors in the United Kingdom *Personal Financial Specialist, a
special financial planning credential granted by the American Institute of
Certified Public Accountants (AICPA) to CPAs who meet certain requirements
*Primerica Financial Services, the largest independent financial services
company in North Ameroca

'Medicine': *Patellofemoral Syndrome, a type of knee disorder *Progression Free
Survival, time without tumor progression in oncology
* Post-Finasteride Syndrome

'Technology': *Perfect forward secrecy, a property in cryptography *, an early
PC word processor *Planetary Fourier Spectrometer, an infrared spectrometer.
Used by European Space Agency on their Venus Express Mission *Playstation File
System, the filesystem used on the PlayStation 2 hard drive *Professional File
System, a third-party filesystem used on the Amiga

'Other': *Peace and Friendship Stadium, an Indoor sports Arena in Piraeus,
Athens, Greece *Penang Free School, a well-recognized English school in
Malaysia, in the state of Penang *Petrol Filling Station, more commonly known
simply as a filling, fueling, gasoline/gas, petrol or service station, or even
garage. *Philadelphia Folksong Society, a Philadelphia organization promoting
folk music *Picture Frame Seduction, a Welsh punk rock band *PlaysForSure, a
marketing certification given by Microsoft to media players *Pool Filter Sand,
aquarium substrate or filter media for sand filter *Princeton Friends School, a
coeducational Quaker school in Princeton Township, New Jersey
